链接词：
总之：to conclude= in conclusion
显然:Obviously
此外:Futhermore
反过来：in turn
目前:currently
在我看来:in my point of view= From where i stand= As for me
例如：For instance
首先：first and foremost= to begin with= for starters= for one things
毫无疑问:There is no doubt
总的来说:overall
鉴于上述好处：given the benefits outlined above
这一名言显示了:The saying shows
我认为：I deam
